    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#mobilityDataStandard> <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap/mobility-data-standard/other>;
    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#dataFormatNotes> "Data model based on the RDF W3C standard https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf11-primer/\r\nData format is JSON-LD (Linked Data) and the grammar is RDF"@de, "Data model based on the RDF W3C standard https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf11-primer/\r\nData format is JSON-LD (Linked Data) and the grammar is RDF"@en, "Data model based on the RDF W3C standard https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf11-primer/\r\nData format is JSON-LD (Linked Data) and the grammar is RDF"@fr, "Data model based on the RDF W3C standard https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf11-primer/\r\nData format is JSON-LD (Linked Data) and the grammar is RDF"@nl
