    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This dataset provides the weekly schedule of shuttle bus services from Stop Lille Airport. Each record represents a single bus tour with detailed stop information, departure time, price and the corresponding day of the week.\r\n\r\ndepartureDay is a numeric value indicating the weekday of the departure:\r\n\r\n0 = Monday\r\n1 = Tuesday\r\n2 = Wednesday\r\n3 = Thursday\r\n4 = Friday\r\n5 = Saturday\r\n6 = Sunday\r\n\r\nThe data is suitable for integration into multimodal journey planners, passenger information systems, and mobility apps."@en;
