    <https://w3id.org/mobilitydcat-ap#dataFormatNotes> "## Request examples: ##\r\n/pub/location  \r\npub/location/52  \r\npub/location?locations=52,53,13  \r\n \r\n## Response: A location object or a list of location objects ##\r\n>{   \r\n>>\"id\": 48,   \r\n>>\"type\": 1,  \r\n>>\"name\": \"Station Antwerpen-Centraal\",  \r\n>>\"latitude\": \"51.217611000000\",   \r\n>>\"longitude\": \"4.421000000000\",  \r\n>>\"bikes_available\": 76,  \r\n>>\"bikes_in_use\": 34,  \r\n>>\"last_seen\": \"2020-12-17T14:42:23\"  \r\n\r\n>},   \r\n \r\n### field Type Description ###\r\nid INT The unique identifier for a location  \r\ntype INT Type of the location 1. normal lock location 2. Smartlock location  \r\nname STRING The name of the location  \r\nlatitude NUMBER Geo location  \r\nlongitude NUMBER Geo location  \r\nbikes_available INT Number of bike available  \r\nbikes_in_use INT Number of bikes on their way  \r\nlast_seen DATETIME Last sync from location  "@en
}
